---
title: One Pot Peri-Peri Prawns with Couscous
description: Peri Peri. The Portuguese marinade so delicious, they named it twice. Our Portuguese-inspired peri-peri prawns are quick, delicious and simple to cook, making them a great thing to enjoy for a midweek dinner. Packed with fresh ingredients like courgette, sun-dried tomatoes and red onion, the flavours in this dish are hard to beat. Serve everything up in deep bowls and finish off with a good squeeze of fresh zesty lemon.
